column6: "LET GO" Wait. Secret Avengers actually had a plan? And it worked? Or NOT EXACTLY? The Fury meets its babies. Black Widow & Lady Bulllseye -- where are they? Spider-Woman's gift can change everything. We made some beautiful splash pages, but the ones in this issue -- or is it the next one -- oh, just you wait.
